  <brief_title>Use of Electroconvulsive Therapy (ECT) in Chronic, Severe, Treatment Resistant Posttraumatic Stress Disorder</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of ECT in Chronic, Severe, Antidepressant- And CBT-Refractory Posttraumatic Stress Disorder: An Open, Prospective Study</official_title>
